			<div class="article-title col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-8 pv-sm">
				<h1 class="txt-f4 txt-s7 balance-text">International vulnerabilities and opportunities for Australia’s universities</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="article-author pv-md col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6">
															<a class="txt-dn txt-f1 txt-s3 txt-tu" href="/the-interpreter/contributors/articles/melissa-conley-tyler">
							Melissa Conley Tyler
						</a>
												</div>
							<div class="article-summary col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-10">
					<p class="txt-s5 txt-f1 balance-text txt-lmd">
						Universities need to accept their vulnerability to internationalisation in order to prepare students for the future.
					</p>
				</div>
					</div>

		<div class="article-main-image">
			<img class="article-main-image-img" src="https://www.lowyinstitute.org/sites/default/files/styles/interpreter_article_image/public/12495789215_78312281f8_k-mini.jpg?itok=3sWS4a_q" alt="Photo: AnveshPandra/Flickr">
              <div class="article-save-btn">
          
        </div>
