    <a class="article-thumb-wrap" href="/the-interpreter/facebook-short-guide-ambassadors">
      <div class="article-thumb"
           style="background-image: url('https://www.lowyinstitute.org/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/facebook.jpg?itok=8kL_4DV2'">
       </div>
    </a>

    <div class="article-title">
      <h3>
        <a href="/the-interpreter/facebook-short-guide-ambassadors">
          Facebook: A short guide for ambassadors
        </a>
      </h3>
    </div>

    <div class="pv-sm">
      <div class="article-precede">
        My research into how diplomatic missions use Facebook has identified four forms of communication that Ambassadors can attempt.
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</div>
													

<div class="col-sm-4">
